Example using Markdown as canonical format to test alternative ways to write instruction blocks.

# New instruction

No content, closing pipe:

:::{new}

:::

Single new block:

:::{new}

New paragraph #1

:::

Multiple new blocks:

:::{new}

New paragraph #2

New paragraph #3

:::

# Edit instruction

Edit next block:

:::{edit}

Paragraph to edit #1

:::

Edit muliple blocks:

:::{edit}

Paragraph to edit #4

Paragraph to edit #5

:::
